    "description": "<div>Welcome to <i>Melting Pot</i>, hosted by Kim Paris on Freeform Portland. Melting Pot highlights the positive power of music, to help us stay upbeat in these turbulent times. Kim Paris hosts Melting Pot every other Sunday morning, 8-10 am on <a href=\"https://www.freeformportland.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Freeform Portland</a>.\u00a0<br /></div><div><br /></div><div>This episode is called <i>Relics &amp; Rarities</i>, a mix of lesser-known and hard to find tracks from my music collection. Included are rare tracks by Abel Zarate, Bobby Hutcherson, Steely Dan, Pink Floyd and more! This episode aired on 7/24/22.</div><div><br /></div><div>Freeform Portland is a low-power nonprofit, independent, community-driven radio station broadcasting live at KFFP-LP 90.3 FM, KFFD-LP 98.3 FM &amp; KYQT-LP 101.5 FM in the Portland metro area, and streaming online at <a href=\"https://freeformportland.org/listen\" rel=\"nofollow\">freeformportland.org/listen</a>.</div><div><br /></div><div><div>The set list for this show is posted as a .png file.</div><div><br /></div><div>More Freeform Portland radio shows are available here: <a href=\"https://archive.org/details/fmradioarchive?query=freeform+portland\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://archive.org/details/fmradioarchive?query=freeform+portland</a></div></div><div><div style=\"color:rgb(44,44,44);font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br /></div><div style=\"color:rgb(44,44,44);font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"g0msgRLsASO4KZPYAmWYAkcwP8HsFCcUXp1wvAAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\" style=\"border:0px;vertical-align:middle;height:auto;\" /></div></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div>",
